<div class="row centered-text content animated fadeIn">
  <h2 class="subheader">What does ARiiP do?</h2>
  <div class="small-12 columns centered-text home_box">
    <h6>
    <strong>ARiiP</strong> is an Integration Platform that allows Developers and Tech Users to easily integrate any Input source (ex: CSV, SQL, XML, JSON,..) with any Output (ex: SQL, CSV, JSON, XML, Services, Email, File,..) in real-time - for both local and/or cloud Inputs and Outputs.
    </h6>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns home_box">
        <%= link_to 'Learn how ARiiP works', {:controller => '/how', :action => 'index'}, :class => 'button large expand radius warning icon-how' %>
