    <h5>Integrate Everything</h5>
    <p class="small-text">Easily integrate whatever data &amp; service you want: CRM, ERP, Forms, Social Media, Own Applications, among others. With ARiiP you can connect anything based on the technology used and not on the platform.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns home_box ">
